```(ib_venv3) C02C185TMD6T:core-platform-service heymian$ aws --version

Ah, yeah, I think that's it. You'd need to update to AWS CLI v2
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/cli/latest/userguide/getting-started-install.html
I'll add that to the FAQ and make that more clear on the setup doc
